FormatText.string: Aurelia Hammerlock, Sir Hammerlock's sister and CEO of the Jakobs Corporation, is offering to pay you to leave Eden-6. She's invited you to Jakobs Manor to negotiate. It's almost certainly a trap. It's also the only way to find the Eden-6 Vault Key.
